title: Ep. 76 - Looking Beyond the Fed Noise
itunes:title: Looking Beyond the Fed Noise
description: Franks' guests include S&A Editors Dr. David Eifig and Braden Copeland. Eifrig discusses opportunities in the muni-bond market. Copeland talks about the Fed and what the end of QE2 means for stocks.
